### API Endpoints for category ----------------------------------------------------

### Add New Category Document
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categories": [
    { "name": "Dairy", "quantity": 10 },
    { "name": "Meats", "quantity": 5 },
    { "name": "Fruits", "quantity": 15 }
  ]
}

### Get All Category Documents
GET http://localhost:5000/api/categories

### Update a Category Document by ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/categories/category/update/6834534b45f1268d805dc104
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categories": [
    {
      "CatId": "60c72b559e1d4c4f887fd321",
      "quantity": 20
    }
  ]
}

### Delete a Category Document by ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/categories/categories/6834534b45f1268d805dc108
