### Order API endpoints -----------------------------------------------------------

### Retrieve all orders in database
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders

### Create New Order 
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "60c72b2f9e1d4c4f887fd123",
  "products": [
    {
      "productId": "60c72b559e1d4c4f887fd124",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "60c72b559e1d4c4f887fd125",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "total": 150
}

### Get All Orders by User ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/user/6834639992b385f4d35031a7

### Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/6835a64ba4aee8a63d348ec4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Shipped"
}

### Delete Order
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/orders/6834648992b385f4d35031b9

